

## ğŸ“Œ Project Overview
The Agriculture Guidance System is a mobile application designed to assist farmers in selecting and managing crops based on climate conditions, land size, and seasonal patterns.  
The system provides complete crop lifecycle guidance with voice support in Telugu and English to support rural and uneducated farmers.

---

## ğŸ¯ Problem Statement
Farmers lack timely climate-based guidance for crop selection, pest control, and resource planning, leading to low productivity and financial losses.  
There is a need for a voice-enabled smart agriculture application that provides end-to-end crop lifecycle support, land-based input calculations, and insect management in local languages.

---

## ğŸš€ Key Features

### ğŸŒ Climate-Based Crop Recommendation
- GPS-based location detection
- Real-time weather integration
- Seasonal crop suggestions
- Ranked recommendations (Best, Good, Risky)

### ğŸŒ± Land Size-Based Resource Calculator
- Input land in acres
- Automatic calculation of seed, fertilizer, water, and pesticide requirements
- Cost estimation for inputs
- Expected yield and profit estimation

### ğŸ“… Crop Lifecycle Management
- Day-by-day guidance from land preparation to harvest
- Stage tracking (Sowing, Germination, Vegetative, Flowering, Fruiting, Harvest)
- Daily reminders with voice alerts
- Task completion tracking

### ğŸ› Insect & Pest Management Module
- Symptom-based pest identification
- Organic and chemical treatment suggestions
- Dosage calculation based on land size
- Safety instructions for pesticide usage
- Preventive pest risk alerts

### ğŸ’§ Smart Irrigation Advisory
- Weather-based irrigation suggestions
- Heatwave, rain, and frost alerts
- Stage-based watering guidance

### ğŸ“Š Cost & Profit Tracking
- Seed, fertilizer, pesticide, and labor tracking
- Total investment calculation
- Estimated yield and profit dashboard

### ğŸ“¶ Offline Support
- Offline crop guidance
- Stored voice instructions
- Internet required only for weather updates

