## ğŸ›  Technology Stack (Suggested)
- Frontend: Android (Java/Kotlin) or Flutter
- Backend: Spring Boot (Java)
- Database: MySQL / Firebase
- APIs: Weather API, Google Text-to-Speech, Speech Recognition API

